    99 Speed Mart Sdn Bhd Vacancies TRAINEE ASSISTANT WAREHOUSE MANAGER

    November 19, 2020

    TOC

    • Job Description
    • Company Overview
    • How To Apply

    99 Speed Mart Sdn Bhd is looking for new potential candidates to fill in for TRAINEE ASSISTANT WAREHOUSE MANAGER position. If you currently looking for new job opportunities and qualified with the job desc, feel free to apply this job.

    Job Description

    Job Descriptions
    • Manage and control the daily warehouse operation job
    • Ensure the timely shipping and receiving of all the products or goods
    • Ensure that all orders are completed on time and ready for collection or delivery
    • Maintain the operations by preparing and implementing the policies or standards in order to meet the requirement of the company
    • Provide assistance in completing the warehouse operational requirements by scheduling and assigning the employees
    • Maintaining the warehouse staff by recruiting, selecting, orienting and training the employees
    • Provide assistance in personnel, training and development, safety, technical and operation matters
    • Handle and coordinate all the relevant activities and job
    • Work with internal and external team closely in order to run the activities smoothly
    • Ensure the physical condition of warehouse, equipment, vehicle(lorry or forklift) and other related from time to time
    • Ensure the safety and cleanliness of the environment of warehouse
    • Protect employees by providing a safe and clean environment
    • Responsible on reporting all the information or decision to Warehouse Manager
    • Able to undertake the ad-hoc tasks and related duties as and when required from time to time which assigned by the superior or manager
    Requirements
    • Candidates must possess at least Degree in Business or Logistics or related field
    • Having experience in logistics or warehousing will be an added advantage
    • Able to travel outstation or transferable
    • Possess its own transport
    • Strong Communication Skill
    • Positive attitude and passionate on the collaborative teamwork
    • Possess strong organization skills and planning abilities
    Benefits
    • Annual Bonus
    • Annual Increment
    • Opportunity of Promotion
    • Entitlement of EPF, Socso and EIS
    • Training will be provided
    • Panel Clinic will be provided

    Company Overview

    99 SPEEDMART SDN BHD was established in 1987 in the form of a traditional "mom and pop" sundry shop. For now, 99 speedmart has operated more than 1000 outlets and keep expanding with employ more than 4500 people. We are one of the market leader in grocery market of Malaysia currently.
